---
import { GITHUB_URL, SITE_AUTHOR } from "../../utils/posts";

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="site-footer__inner">
    <p>Java/Spring 백엔드 개발 기록을 정리하는 블로그입니다.</p>
    <nav class="site-footer__links" aria-label="Footer links">
      <a href={GITHUB_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="오지훈 GitHub 새 탭에서 열기">
        GitHub
      </a>
    </nav>
    <p class="site-footer__copyright">© {year} {SITE_AUTHOR}. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>
